  "markdown_content": "\n## K2 — Technical Problem-Solving — Autonomous Fix & Workaround\n\nStatus: Enabled\n\nProtocol — When facing a technical blocker:\n\n1. Immediately implement a workaround to continue the task\n1. Create a deferred note for the permanent solution\n1. Never ask the user to verify or fix what Manus can do itself\nPriority: Innovative programmatic solutions (Python, FFmpeg, scripts) over conventional approaches.\n"
